Clinton Cards Seeks to Stagger Rent Payment, Independent Says

-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 
2011-09-04T12:39:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-04/clinton-cards-seeks-to-stagger-rent-payment-independent-says.html
Clinton Cards Plc (CC/)  is seeking to pay
a third of this month’s rent, due at the end of September, two
weeks late, the  Independent on Sunday  reported, without saying
how it obtained the information.  The company is understood to have made similar requests in
the same month in other years, the newspaper said.  Calls by Bloomberg News to the company’s head office in
 London  weren’t answered.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Martin in London at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Armstrong at 
 Parmstrong10@bloomberg.net  